{"tid":1176690,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實炑八燒肉係咪要跑套餐數？","createTime":"2019-05-29T11:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T15:46:27.000Z","uid":165939,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67e62422290c52bf5054f76ec0f4cb5b9acb9dc5","tid":1176690,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:28:11.000Z","msg":"我次次去職員都問我要唔要嗌餐，但個set 永遠都好唔吸引。<br />\n<br />\n試過一次職員又係叫我嗌餐，聲稱會執啲靚嘅位俾我，結果全部都係勁難食，勁難咬開，仲貴過散嗌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住有一次醒啦，去第二間分店食，唔嗌餐。但聽到有個職員全程sell 隔離枱嗌餐，又係講返一樣嘅嘢。「你鍾意食啲咩位，我盡量執返俾你」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離枱有大約8個人，個staff 全程係咁sell, 最搞笑係食食下隔離枱有幾個大人出去食支煙先，得返兩三個後生仔，跟住個職員一路幫佢地燒啲大件嘅肉，然後再同個後生仔講，「你睇下你地夠唔夠食啦，唔夠可以再嗌下啲餐」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生仔表示自己冇決定權，都係要等大人返嚟再話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到佢地食完煙返嚟，個staff 又攞返本menu 去問啲大人，洗唔洗再加啲餐食啊，有醬油蟹喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講已經唔係第一次見到呢個情況，但真係啲套餐又貴又唔好食，點叫得落，到底炑八係咪要keep 住跑套餐啲數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d53f6a623f9bf1501f911af2177f66b46308bf","tid":1176690,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6aba765b2797c6fd56109646245200838de4564e","tid":1176690,"uid":72690,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"咁多選舉，點解仲要去炑八"},{"pid":"cd859745f8843053ade4fbe0ca2e1a611e4d1027","tid":1176690,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多選擇，點解仲要去炑八</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e7db601719f8309491687c02a045bfd95ed277e6","tid":1176690,"uid":12618,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"泡菜野一向辣殺"},{"pid":"7c966e522f5c35a7b69d81c414c4fab6b8d5f08a","tid":1176690,"uid":51521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"得銅鑼灣個間好食啲其他垃圾"},{"pid":"cd54b06decb7f11cf40b059a87c93de1d853f44f","tid":1176690,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"韓燒唔會食炑八啦"},{"pid":"ecf88ebcff11836e1db6f4322fef199116a527bb","tid":1176690,"uid":180402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"得lunch set抵食"},{"pid":"bf625bc2dec3d69a813d4325017b477734fb4527","tid":1176690,"uid":165939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd54b06decb7f11cf40b059a87c93de1d853f44f","tid":1176690,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"韓燒唔會食炑八啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"邊間好"},{"pid":"de8f26ab7a95bd1b0d494f7b8008b06133c68aae","tid":1176690,"uid":165939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecf88ebcff11836e1db6f4322fef199116a527bb","tid":1176690,"uid":180402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"得lunch set抵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"晚餐散嗌如果用app 約定，半價都有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f9c483e6f81544e4e7644e5ef4d21856bd0469","tid":1176690,"uid":43343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早嗰排有個喺炑八做嘅frd喺wtsapp send咗佢地個menu畀我 叫我去幫襯"},{"pid":"a3c250b3eaaaf77426654043f2014070422a22c6","tid":1176690,"uid":237479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"旺角個間有個帶位好靚女"}]}